title: Creators of the Fast and Furious Musical !!
description:
Brad Silnutzer and Joey Orton are the writers, directors, choreographers, and stars of 'The Fast and The Furious Musical Parody,' which just completed its fourth sold-out show in LA. Brad's background is in television and sketch comedy, and Joey's is in songwriting. The musical is hilarious, the "Team America" of F&F parodies.

 

This show is also a video: https://youtu.be/2mGiKhQVqTQ
